             Well, it was--
        It was nice meeting you.

14:39.145 --> 14:40.544
  I'm having a nervous--

14:41.247 --> 14:43.247
             --breakdown.

14:43.249 --> 14:46.217
        I'm sorry, Sam.
 I couldn't catch Major Nelson.

14:46.219 --> 14:49.119
    Jim, George, piano.
         I'm back.

