17:09.295 --> 17:11.494
Well, he may not be the only
entertainer in the world,

17:11.497 --> 17:12.896
but he's certainly the greatest.

17:12.897 --> 17:15.199
          Yeah, Roger, it's--
      It's not the entertainment

17:15.201 --> 17:16.900
