17:32.919 --> 17:35.385
Well, it's not the entertainment
    that's important, Tony.

17:35.387 --> 17:37.321
It's the spirit of the occasion
          that counts.

17:37.323 --> 17:38.923
                     Yes.

17:38.925 --> 17:40.090
Well, to think
that the men

17:40.092 --> 17:42.326
       would care enough
    to do a thing like this.

17:42.328 --> 17:44.561
Well, that's the most important
