  that would make me happier.

17:47.166 --> 17:50.934
I first saw him the same day
I got my first star.

17:50.936 --> 17:51.935
               Eh, saw who, sir?

17:51.937 --> 17:54.738
  Sammy Davis Jr.

17:54.740 --> 17:57.508
    That's a day
 I'll never forget.

17:57.510 --> 17:58.976
We went to see his show
that night.

