     gave you the night off.

23:22.601 --> 23:24.401
      It was sure certainly
       nice of them. Ha-ha.

23:24.403 --> 23:26.270
       I can't tell you how much
           I appreciate this.

23:26.272 --> 23:27.805
                     SAMMY:
                Well, thank you,
                    general.

23:27.807 --> 23:30.440
           PETERSON:
    I said it the first time
     and I'll say it again.

23:30.442 --> 23:33.344
 When you're up on that stage,
 you do the work of two people.

23:33.346 --> 23:34.344
        [SAMMY CHUCKLES]

23:40.919 --> 23:42.719
I really think it was
the greatest evening

23:42.721 --> 23:43.988
in the general's life.

23:43.990 --> 23:46.924
Oh, I am pleased that I was
able to help you, master.

23:46.926 --> 23:48.325
          Yeah, well, after all,
                who got me

23:48.327 --> 23:50.094
              into the situation
             in the first place?

23:50.096 --> 23:51.295
                [DOORBELL RINGS]

23:51.297 --> 23:54.265
     Ah, hey, stay out of sight,
           will you? Just--

23:54.267 --> 23:56.166
        Just stay there.

23:56.168 --> 23:57.167
      Huh? Oh, hi, Sammy.

23:57.169 --> 23:58.168
              Hi, Tony.

23:58.170 --> 23:59.570
Well, we were
just talking about

23:59.572 --> 24:01.071
how wonderful you
were last night.

24:01.073 --> 24:02.406
             Well, I'm glad
             you enjoyed it.

24:02.408 --> 24:04.107
   I really appreciate
   what you did for us.

24:04.109 --> 24:06.109
       Then would you mind doing
         a little favor for me?

24:06.111 --> 24:07.377
       Anything.
             Anything at all?

24:07.379 --> 24:09.313
  Oh, sure, anything.
             [CHUCKLES]

24:09.315 --> 24:10.648
       Get rid of him.

24:10.650 --> 24:14.350
     ♪ That old black magic
     Has me in its spell ♪

24:14.352 --> 24:15.719
          ♪ Ooh-ooh ♪

24:15.721 --> 24:18.221
         ♪ That old black magic
        That you weave so well ♪

24:18.223 --> 24:22.392
             [♪♪♪]

